description:
It's the Mandelbulb! What happens when you take the original fractal (The Mandelbrot Set) and extend it into 3D space? And how do you visualize it in Processing (Java) as a point cloud? https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/168-mandelbulb.html
